OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry, fine
OL,6,Fevening, though remaining windy. A
OL,7,Fclear night will follow, and becoming
OL,8,Fchilly in sheltered inland spots.
OL,9,FWinds abating a little, though a brisk
OL,10,Fbreeze persisting.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FFine, dry and sunny, though
OL,13,Frather windy once again, with the
OL,14,Fstrongest winds around the coast. Warm
OL,15,Finland but cooler around the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
