OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FFriday,
OL,6,Fmostly fine, dry and very warm. Chance
OL,7,Fof showers later. Cloudier Saturday
OL,8,Fand Sunday, with the chance of rain or
OL,9,Fshowers, perhaps thundery. Less warm
OL,10,Flater. Generally light winds.
